OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,FA business owner hit hard by the Tube
OL,7,Fstrike said trade was 'completely
OL,8,Fdead' as drivers began industrial
OL,9,Faction.
OL,11,FAnand Majithia has run a locksmith and
OL,12,Fphotography shop in central London for
OL,13,F35 years and has little sympathy with
OL,14,Fdrivers.
OL,16,F"This strike really doesn't make any
OL,17,Fsense", Mr Majithia told ITV News
OL,18,FLondon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,F"If you've been told work less and we
OL,7,Fwill pay you the same why would you
OL,8,Fnot?
OL,10,F"If you've been told instead of
OL,11,Fworking five days, work for four days,
OL,12,Fand you also have a choice of either
OL,13,Faccepting those terms or not - and you
OL,14,Fstill choose to have a strike - people
OL,15,Fare suffering every time there is a
OL,16,Fstrike.
OL,18,FThe RMT union has rejected an offer
OL,19,Ffor drivers to voluntarily work a four
OL,20,Fdays a week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,FDrivers would see the working week cut
OL,7,Ffrom 36 hours to 35 hours and their
OL,8,Fcontractual hours would stay the same
OL,9,Fbecause paid meal breaks would be
OL,10,Fintroduced.
OL,12,FIn practice drivers would work longer
OL,13,Fdays but fewer days each week and
OL,14,Ffewer hours.
OL,16,FAnand Majithia added: "We are the ones
OL,17,Fwho are probably the worst affected,
OL,18,Fbecause staff will go to their work,
OL,19,Fthey'll still get paid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,F"People who own the business will not
OL,7,Fget the business, but they still have
OL,8,Fto find the money to pay the staff.
OL,10,F"So we always suffer, wherever you
OL,11,Flook, we will always suffer.
OL,13,F"But there has to be some logic and
OL,14,Funderstanding.
OL,16,F"Let's be realistic here. The
OL,17,Funderground is not taking money out of
OL,18,Ftheir pockets. They're actually
OL,19,Ftelling them, listen, do what you want
OL,20,Fto do.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,F"I'm sorry, it's hard to swallow."
OL,8,FRMT members are walking out from 12pm
OL,9,Ffor 24 hours on Tuesday and Thursday.
OL,11,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,12,Fsaid: "We have approached negotiations
OL,13,Fwith TfL in good faith throughout this
OL,14,Fentire process, but despite our best
OL,15,Fefforts, TfL seem unwilling to make
OL,16,Fany concessions in a bid to avert
OL,17,Fstrike action.
OL,19,F"This is extremely disappointing and
OL,20,Fhas baffled our negotiators.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,F"The approach of TfL is not one which
OL,7,Fleads to industrial peace and will
OL,8,Finfuriate our members who want to see
OL,9,Fa negotiated settlement to this
OL,10,Favoidable dispute."
OL,12,FTfL said services will vary across
OL,13,Flines and urged passengers to check
OL,14,Fbefore they travel.
OL,16,FSome bus routes in the capital
OL,17,Foperated by Stagecoach will be
OL,18,Faffected by a separate 24-hour strike
OL,19,Ffrom 5am on Friday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,FClaire Mann, TfL's chief operating
OL,7,Fofficer, said: "We have set out
OL,8,Fproposals to the RMT for a four-day
OL,9,Fworking week.
OL,11,F"This allows us to offer train
OL,12,Foperators an additional day off,
OL,13,Fwhilst at the same time bringing
OL,14,FLondon Underground in line with the
OL,15,Fworking patterns of other train
OL,16,Foperating companies, improving
OL,17,Freliability and flexibility at no
OL,18,Fadditional cost.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776874270
OL,3,CTrade 'completely dead' says worried
OL,4,Cbusiness owner as Tube strike begins
OL,6,F"The changes would be voluntary, there
OL,7,Fwould be no reduction in contractual
OL,8,Fhours and those who wish to continue a
OL,9,Ffive-day working week pattern would be
OL,10,Fable to do so."
OL,12,FWhen are the Tube strikes?
